14
00:01:59,400 --> 00:02:00,640
I don't need him to tell me.

15
00:02:00,920 --> 00:02:03,040
I'm experiencing life
in your recruit company now.

16
00:02:03,200 --> 00:02:05,000
I know everything about you guys.

17
