20
00:02:16,680 --> 00:02:18,960
Guohua doesn't understand
the stakes here.

21
00:02:19,320 --> 00:02:21,120
I can't let others attack him with this.

22
00:02:21,360 --> 00:02:23,480
I think it's you who don't understand.

23
00:02:24,080 --> 00:02:25,480
Now everybody is happy,

24
00:02:25,480 --> 00:02:27,080
why do you have to
make it hard for everyone?

25
00:02:27,480 --> 00:02:29,720
We finally got here today.

26
00:02:29,720 --> 00:02:31,720
Now there's a shortcut to go,

27
00:02:31,720 --> 00:02:32,880
why do you have to take that

28
00:02:32,880 --> 00:02:33,920
longer road?

29
00:02:33,920 --> 00:02:35,800
Why do you have to make it hard?

30
00:02:36,560 --> 00:02:38,480
There is no shortcut in this world.

31
00:02:38,960 --> 00:02:41,800
There is a price to pay
for taking the shortcut.

32
00:02:42,960 --> 00:02:43,680
Chunsheng,

33
00:02:44,480 --> 00:02:46,800
sometimes there's nothing wrong with

34
00:02:46,800 --> 00:02:47,960
doing something against the rules.

35
00:02:48,200 --> 00:02:49,720
And everyone already agrees with

36
00:02:49,720 --> 00:02:50,800
doing such a thing,

37
00:02:50,960 --> 00:02:52,440
only you don't agree.

38
00:02:52,800 --> 00:02:53,960
People won't think you are a good person,

39
00:02:53,960 --> 00:02:55,960
they only think you're stupid.

40
00:02:56,200 --> 00:02:57,520
Your old opinions

41
00:02:57,520 --> 00:02:59,680
don't work anymore in this society.

42
00:03:00,920 --> 00:03:01,960
I don't care about others,

43
00:03:02,680 --> 00:03:03,680
but I, myself,

44
00:03:04,200 --> 00:03:05,720
will only take the way I think is right.

45
00:03:06,840 --> 00:03:07,880
I don't want to have regrets.

46
00:03:08,840 --> 00:03:09,520
Stop!

47
00:03:13,720 --> 00:03:14,960
Have you thought about me?

48
00:03:16,120 --> 00:03:16,880
Do you know that

49
00:03:17,080 --> 00:03:18,560
someone told my superior

50
00:03:19,080 --> 00:03:20,680
I was dating an ordinary soldier?

51
00:03:21,720 --> 00:03:23,440
They speak with sarcasm everyday,

52
00:03:23,440 --> 00:03:24,920
but I didn't care.

53
00:03:25,200 --> 00:03:27,440
I work hard every day to improve.

54
00:03:27,440 --> 00:03:29,120
What am I doing this for?

55
00:03:29,560 --> 00:03:30,560
I just want the both of us

56
00:03:30,560 --> 00:03:32,480
to be promoted as soon as possible,

57
00:03:32,560 --> 00:03:34,200
so we can be together without worries.

58
00:03:34,880 --> 00:03:36,200
I'm working hard

59
00:03:36,200 --> 00:03:36,920
for our future,

60
00:03:36,920 --> 00:03:38,160
