Yanqiu.

367
00:23:09,980 --> 00:23:11,580
If we had money,

368
00:23:11,820 --> 00:23:13,540
of course we would settle it.

369
00:23:13,940 --> 00:23:15,100
The factory met some difficulties.

370
00:23:17,780 --> 00:23:20,220
Could you please make an exception

371
00:23:20,500 --> 00:23:22,540
and settle mine first?

372
00:23:22,820 --> 00:23:25,420
Yanqiu, how can you make such a request?

373
00:23:28,020 --> 00:23:29,820
That is unreasonable.

374
00:23:30,220 --> 00:23:33,140
