didn't get their salary yet,

375
00:23:33,140 --> 00:23:35,620
how can you ask me to settle your salary

376
00:23:36,900 --> 00:23:37,900
first?

377
00:23:40,020 --> 00:23:41,820
If my family hadn't had difficulty,

378
00:23:41,820 --> 00:23:43,620
I wouldn't have made such a request.

379
00:23:44,700 --> 00:23:46,460
Everybody has difficulties now.

380
00:23:46,700 --> 00:23:48,940
You are not an exception.

381
00:23:49,260 --> 00:23:51,860
