those vixenish workers.

406
00:24:52,500 --> 00:24:52,860
That's right.

407
00:24:52,860 --> 00:24:54,620
He would give them some money at least.

408
00:24:55,020 --> 00:24:55,380
Yanqiu.

409
00:24:55,380 --> 00:24:56,900
We are being too easy-going.

410
00:24:59,220 --> 00:24:59,900
Qi Tian?

411
00:25:00,900 --> 00:25:01,900
Why are you here?

412
00:25:03,140 --> 00:25:05,260
An old acquaintance
introduced me to a new job.

413
00:25:06,100 --> 00:25:07,300
Today, I delivered

414
00:25:07,300 --> 00:25:08,660
some goods to your factory.

415
00:25:08,700 --> 00:25:10,500
