421
00:25:25,980 --> 00:25:27,060
Enough. Enough for me.

422
00:25:27,060 --> 00:25:28,340
You gave me too much. You should...

423
00:25:28,340 --> 00:25:30,500
- I can't eat so much.
- Save some for yourself.

424
00:25:30,780 --> 00:25:32,300
- Enough.
- Your job is tiring.

425
00:25:32,380 --> 00:25:33,620
You should eat a lot,

426
