you won't have enough strength.

427
00:25:57,300 --> 00:25:57,980
Take this.

428
00:25:58,420 --> 00:25:59,060
What are you doing?

429
00:26:01,140 --> 00:26:02,260
I heard what you said.

430
00:26:02,500 --> 00:26:03,700
Just take it.

431
00:26:04,460 --> 00:26:05,780
