444
00:26:55,740 --> 00:26:56,380
Chunsheng?

445
00:26:56,460 --> 00:26:57,700
Look what I brought you.

446
00:26:57,780 --> 00:26:59,220
It's dried sweet potatoes from home.

447
00:26:59,380 --> 00:27:01,020
I know you like it,
so I brought you some.

448
00:27:01,700 --> 00:27:03,780
Come, share it with everyone.

449
00:27:04,060 --> 00:27:05,540
You'll all get some.

450
00:27:05,540 --> 00:27:06,380
Really?

451
00:27:06,380 --> 00:27:07,300
Of course.

452
00:27:07,300 --> 00:27:08,140
Hongling,

453
00:27:09,260 --> 00:27:10,140
this is...

454
00:27:11,380 --> 00:27:12,180
