455
00:27:12,900 --> 00:27:13,700
Ma'am,

456
00:27:14,620 --> 00:27:16,180
I am Xiao Chunsheng,
a soldier of the elite squad

457
00:27:16,340 --> 00:27:18,540
who is about to be
assigned to the 11th Army.

458
00:27:18,780 --> 00:27:19,860
After the recruit company is disbanded,

459
00:27:20,060 --> 00:27:20,740
our elite squad

460
00:27:20,860 --> 00:27:22,940
will go to the military region
for final combat training.

461
00:27:23,660 --> 00:27:25,820
So I'm taking this chance
to visit Hongling.

462
00:27:27,500 --> 00:27:28,580
Hongling and I

463
00:27:28,860 --> 00:27:29,940
grew up together.

464
00:27:30,900 --> 00:27:32,420
You grew up together?

465
00:27:32,420 --> 00:27:33,020
Yes.

466
00:27:33,780 --> 00:27:34,740
Here, ma'am.

467
00:27:34,860 --> 00:27:35,580
Try this.

468
00:27:36,140 --> 00:27:36,900
I'm good. Thank you.

469
00:27:38,020 --> 00:27:40,460
Ma'am, I have to ask you

470
00:27:40,460 --> 00:27:41,940
to take care of Hongling,

471
00:27:42,420 --> 00:27:43,780
otherwise, I wouldn't know

472
00:27:43,940 --> 00:27:45,300
how to face her mother.

473
00:27:47,180 --> 00:27:48,860
