476
00:27:53,260 --> 00:27:53,900
You take your time.

477
00:27:54,180 --> 00:27:54,620
OK.

478
00:27:55,580 --> 00:27:57,140
Chen Can, come with me.

479
00:28:03,100 --> 00:28:04,700
You are really not Hongling's boyfriend?

480
00:28:04,860 --> 00:28:05,940
Boyfriend?

481
00:28:06,540 --> 00:28:08,340
