between Hongling and me.

483
00:28:11,460 --> 00:28:12,980
Revolutionary friendship?

484
00:28:14,060 --> 00:28:16,620
Comrade Xiao, you came at the right time.

485
00:28:16,740 --> 00:28:17,340
You don't know,

486
00:28:17,580 --> 00:28:18,460
that girl just now

