that you were dating someone.

517
00:29:27,780 --> 00:29:30,060
Of course I'd come to help you.

518
00:29:31,140 --> 00:29:32,220
You are really good at making up stories.

519
00:29:32,220 --> 00:29:33,020
We grew up together?

520
00:29:33,020 --> 00:29:34,260
Are you serious??

521
00:29:34,500 --> 00:29:36,700
You grew up together with Ye Fang,
Xiaomei and the others.

522
00:29:37,300 --> 00:29:38,700
I just made that up.

523
00:29:43,460 --> 00:29:44,060
Chunsheng,

524
00:29:46,180 --> 00:29:47,020
sooner or later,

525
00:29:47,340 --> 00:29:49,340
I'll tell everyone

526
00:29:49,660 --> 00:29:50,820
you are my boyfriend.

527
00:29:59,460 --> 00:30:00,020
Let's go.

528
00:30:23,380 --> 00:30:23,900
Shoot.

529
00:30:24,100 --> 00:30:26,060
Director Liu, we are waiting for you.

530
00:30:26,060 --> 00:30:27,220
What's taking you so long?

531
00:30:27,220 --> 00:30:28,260
Listen,

532
00:30:31,580 --> 00:30:33,500
I was being too merciful last time

533
00:30:33,660 --> 00:30:35,380
by not winning all your money.

534
00:30:35,820 --> 00:30:37,620
Today, I will win all your money over.

535
00:30:38,220 --> 00:30:40,580
All right, my money is waiting for you.

536
00:30:40,700 --> 00:30:41,660
Just hurry up.

537
00:30:41,900 --> 00:30:43,020
We are all waiting for you.

538
00:30:43,580 --> 00:30:44,100
Coming.

539
00:31:13,180 --> 00:31:16,100
(Beijing Chunhui Textile Factory)

540
00:31:23,380 --> 00:31:25,300
I can't believe you guys.

541
00:31:25,700 --> 00:31:27,700
You couldn't wait to win my money, huh?

542
00:31:28,300 --> 00:31:30,620
